<h1>FlamesCP</h1>
<hr>
<p>a lightweight mysql-free minecraft control panel for single servers</p>
<br>
<h3>Notes</h3>
<p>Please move the authentication directory (security) to /var/www/security, if you would like to test this.</p>
<p>o.php is the console output reader - do not remove it!</p>
<p> </p>
<p>The daemons are in the DAEMON directory - please start a screen for each and start them up seperately.</p>
<p>Make sure you run the daemons as root!</p>
